WEBVTT

00:10:28.721 --> 00:10:33.481
even when they doubled
and tripled the doses.

00:10:34.632 --> 00:10:37.913
In Mumbai, I met another whistleblower

00:10:37.937 --> 00:10:41.063
from a company that
I had believed was ethical.

00:10:41.764 --> 00:10:45.649
He sat there and described
the well-oiled machinery

00:10:45.673 --> 00:10:47.510
of data manipulation

00:10:47.534 --> 00:10:51.722
his company used to get
compromised drugs approved fast.

00:10:52.537 --> 00:10:56.055
With tears running down
his cheeks, he said,

00:10:56.079 --> 00:10:58.054
"What's going on in the industry

00:10:58.078 --> 00:11:01.596
is very, very, very dirty."